MathSimple - Tiny CLI programs to do math
=========================================

This is a collection of mathematical programs. These programs are like short bc
scripts, but in C with a defined command-line interface (CLI) and using
floating point precision. They do depend on C standard library and some in
cblas.

MathSimple is free software: you can redistribute it and/or modify it under the
terms of the GNU General Public License.

These programs are distributed in the hope that they will be useful, but
WITHOUT ANY WARRANTY; without even the implied warranty of MERCHANTABILITY or
